330/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.poster.avif?t=1729080155\" width=616 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148330/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.webm?t=1729080155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148330/extras/33a1b537bf43781d022f44625dd82ac7.mp4?t=1729080155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cards are your weapons</h2><br>Use the elements of the cards in the open world to take advantage of situations or make a powerful quick hand to take any collector out of your way!",
